.LI "\*LSgNDropPocketActivePixel\*O"
Specifies the color for the background of the DropPocket when a
droppable icon is above the DropPocket.
.LI "\*LSgNiconDataBasePath\*O"
Specifies the location of the icon database.  The default value is
/usr/lib/filetype/workspace.ctr.  Setting this resource to a filename
that is not a legal icon database will cause serious problems for the
DropPocket.
.LI "\*LSgNname\*O"
Specifies the compound string that is the name of the current icon.
By setting this resource, the application can control the initial icon
that appears in the DropPocket.  If this resource is NULL, the
DropPocket will appear empty. Refer to \*LXmString(3X)\*O for more
information on the creation and structure of compound strings.
